As whitepilled as it makes you feel 

feeling like you’re on the right side of some great spiritual battle doesn’t make you remotely unique. Doesn’t mean it’s wrong. One side can be objectively better and it’s good to be on that side.

All zuby wasn’t even really talking about a religious war, e.g., isis vs Christians. That’s not even a battle that’s happening. He’s acting like there’s a spiritual divide between Libs and his ingroup (basically neocons). Alright dude
I don’t agree with her ideologically but this point isn’t half bad. And dunking on Zuby is usually good in my book. He seems like an opportunist, grifter, from what I’ve seen.

It is, actually. 

And shades of grey exist
Btw we’re deep into Kali Yuga and will be for thousands, and thousands of years.
